snippet.title: Unbox - Greenlight Trailer
snippet.description:
The ultimate postal service has arrived... self-delivering cardboard boxes! We need you and your friends to test this revolutionary technology before it goes to market: It's time to Roll, Jump and Unbox to Victory!

-----------------------------

We're on Greenlight and need your votes! Head to http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=519179923  and check out our website: http://www.unboxgame.com
